FBIS4-39508 "drsov110_b_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin, Grachev at Emergency Meeting on N. Caucasus Yeltsin, Grachev at Emergency Meeting on N. Caucasus LD0706155194 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 1500 GMT 7 Jun 94 LD0706155194 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] President Yeltsin is holding an emergency meeting to discuss the aggravation of the situation in the North Caucasus. According to information available to Ekho Moskvy radio, the meeting is being attended by Defense Minister Pavel Grachev and Oleg Lobov, secretary of the Russian Security Council.
